// DERIVATIONAL MORPHOLOGY RULES
// USED FOR DETERMINING THE CATEGORY OF THE WORD
// FORMAT OF RULE
// SUFFIX <suffix> ROOTCAT <rcat> THEN <pcat>
// rcat is category of stem formed after removing suffix
// pcat is the list of possible categories if rcat is matched
// multiple categories is pcat are seperated by commas
SUFFIX कर ROOTCAT verb THEN verb
SUFFIX के ROOTCAT verb THEN verb
SUFFIX ता ROOTCAT adjective THEN noun
SUFFIX मय ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective
SUFFIX मयी ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective
SUFFIX कश ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective
SUFFIX वाला ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective,noun
SUFFIX वाली ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective,noun
SUFFIX वाले ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective,noun 
SUFFIX वालाें ROOTCAT noun THEN adjective,noun 
SUFFIX में ROOTCAT pronoun THEN adverb 
SUFFIX नेवाला ROOTCAT verb THEN adjective,noun
SUFFIX नेवाली ROOTCAT verb THEN adjective,noun
SUFFIX नेवाले ROOTCAT verb THEN adjective,noun 
SUFFIX नेवालाें ROOTCAT verb THEN adjective,noun 
SUFFIX पन ROOTCAT adjective THEN noun 
SUFFIX नामा ROOTCAT noun THEN noun 
SUFFIX नामे ROOTCAT noun THEN noun 
SUFFIX नामों ROOTCAT noun THEN noun 
SUFFIX वां ROOTCAT cardinal THEN ordinal 
SUFFIX वें ROOTCAT cardinal THEN ordinal 
SUFFIX वे ROOTCAT cardinal THEN ordinal 
SUFFIX वीं ROOTCAT cardinal THEN ordinal 
SUFFIX वी ROOTCAT cardinal THEN ordinal 
SUFFIX पूर्वक ROOTCAT noun THEN adverb
SUFFIX स्वरूप ROOTCAT noun THEN adverb
SUFFIX वाँ ROOTCAT cardinal THEN ordinal

 